# Dockerfile
# ----------
# Instructions to build the backend container.

# Implementation Checklist:
# 1. Use a base image (e.g., `python:3.10-slim`).
# 2. Set the working directory.
# 3. Copy `requirements.txt` and install dependencies.
# 4. Copy the application code.
# 5. Expose the port (8000).
# 6. Define the command to run the FastAPI app (`uvicorn`).
